headline: T. Rowe Price Q1-2025 Preview: This Still Isn't The Time To Pick Up Shares
summary: T. Rowe Price has struggled with turning the ship around in terms of the AUM outflows, with 13 quarters of AUM outflows. Read more on why I rate TROW a Hold.
